{"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllLinkComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent010ExpandLinkB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent04LinkB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent08LinkMonoB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","level":2},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for link component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomLinkComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the link component tokens you want.","","        override var sizeMinHeightMedium: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._600 }","","        override var colorChevronHover: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { colors.repositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","","        override var spaceColumnGapIconSmall: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingInlineSpacious }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomLinkComponentTokensProvider: LinkComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hunders of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Then, you can give this ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomLinkComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" to your own theme implementation:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(link: CustomLinkComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"or to an already existing theme for example:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    OrangeTheme(link: CustomLinkComponentTokensProvider())"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    let linkComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, color and space semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let linkComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                colors: CustomColorSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                space: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider())"]},{"type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.9.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","name":"Since"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of links","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"link","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSLink"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllLinkComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"LinkComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"links","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Link","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Class","symbolKind":"class","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B32ThemeLinkComponentTokensProviderC","title"